Configuration Paths:

    * samba (fileshares):               /etc/samba/
    * cswwinbind (AD authentication):   /etc/opt/csw/samba/
    * krb5:                             /etc/krb5/

    * dns_secondary:                    /etc/named.conf
                                        /var/named

    * backups:                          /root/backup_script.sh
    * crontab (for root backups):       /var/spool/cron/crontabs/root

    * apache:                           /etc/apache/2.2/httpd.conf
                                        /var/apache/2.2/htdocs/index.html

    * ntp:                              /etc/inet/ntp.conf


    * skel:                             /etc/skel/
